WEBVTT

00:11:58.721 --> 00:12:00.848
This is achievable.

00:12:01.909 --> 00:12:06.028
And we have the talent
to make it a reality.

00:12:06.052 --> 00:12:10.039
But the journey to ready that talent
for the task ahead,

00:12:10.063 --> 00:12:11.730
like my own journey,

00:12:11.754 --> 00:12:13.000
is far too long.

00:12:14.674 --> 00:12:19.107
For the next generation
of African creative leaders,

00:12:19.131 --> 00:12:22.566
we have to shorten
and streamline that journey.

00:12:23.106 --> 00:12:24.492
But most importantly --

00:12:24.516 --> 00:12:26.839
and I cannot stress this enough --

00:12:26.863 --> 00:12:29.141
we have to build their design confidence

00:12:29.165 --> 00:12:33.358
and empower them to develop solutions
that are truly African